query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 0 AND q.view_count <= 100
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('data-structures',
'doctrine-orm',
'drop-down-menu',
'foreach',
'listbox',
'meteor',
'properties',
'recursion',
'reference',
'routing',
'selenium',
'spring-data-jpa',
'sql');
